  <entry>
    <title>Hexo and minos</title>
    <link href="https://mjc-alex.github.io/2023/05/23/Hexo-and-minos/"/>
    <id>https://mjc-alex.github.io/2023/05/23/Hexo-and-minos/</id>
    <published>2023-05-22T16:04:44.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-05-22T16:21:45.576Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<html><head></head><body><p><img src="/2023/05/23/Hexo-and-minos/godfather.png"><br>The image is write as <code>![](/2023/05/23/Hexo-and-minos/godfather.png)</code></p><h2 id="About-Hexo"><a href="#About-Hexo" class="headerlink" title="About Hexo"></a>About Hexo</h2><p>21.5.23, 我建立了我的第一个（正式的）博客，用的是Github + Hexo. 开头很顺利，今天换主题的时候有些小bug。在此记录过程，方便以后迁移。</p><ul><li><p><code>install node.js, git, hexo</code></p>  <figure class="highlight bash hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm i hexo-cli -g</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo -v <span class="hljs-comment"># to check for successful installation</span></span><br><span class="line">$ hexo init &lt;<span class="hljs-built_in">dir</span> name&gt;</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install ...</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo g <span class="hljs-comment"># generate static web page</span></span><br><span class="line">$ hexo s <span class="hljs-comment"># start local serve to preview, ctrl + click the url to open it</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li><li><p><code>connect your github</code></p>  <figure class="highlight bash hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name <span class="hljs-string">"zz2summer"</span> </span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email <span class="hljs-string">"xxxxx@163.com"</span></span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="hljs-string">"summer2zz@163.com"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>  open github, click settings &gt; SSH and GPG keys, create a new ssh key.</p>  <figure class="highlight bash hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="hljs-built_in">cat</span> ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>  copy the output to the new ssh key.</p></li><li><p><code>modify blog/_config.yml</code><br>  open _config.yml, change the last line:</p>  <figure class="highlight bash hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="hljs-built_in">type</span>: git</span><br><span class="line">repository: git@...</span><br><span class="line">branch: main</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="Write-new-blog"><a href="#Write-new-blog" class="headerlink" title="Write new blog"></a>Write new blog</h2><figure class="highlight bash hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm i hexo-deployer-git <span class="hljs-comment"># install a new plugin</span></span><br><span class="line">$ hexo new post <span class="hljs-string">"title"</span> <span class="hljs-comment"># create a new blog</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>Then open blog/source/_posts, there will be a new file named <code>title.md</code></p><figure class="highlight bash hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g -d <span class="hljs-comment"># generate the web page and push new change to github</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>If needed to upload images, modify _config.yml:<br><code>post_assert_folder: true</code></p><h2 id="Delete-blog"><a href="#Delete-blog" class="headerlink" title="Delete blog"></a>Delete blog</h2><p>delete blog/source/_posts/delete.md, and run <code>hexo d -g</code></p></body></html>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
